getGapalign

public Boolean getGapalign()
Gets the gapalign value for this InputParameters.

Returns:
gapalign * Gapalign [This is a true/false setting that tells the program the perform optimised alignments within regions involving gaps. If set to true, the program will perform an alignment using gaps. Otherwise, if it is set to false, it will report only individual HSP where two sequence match each other, and thus will not produce alignments with gaps.]
